description.p:
The invention discloses an improved process for preparing non-hygroscopic Azithromycin dihydrate which comprises -
(a) Preparation of a suspension of Azithromycin monohydrate in any conventional manner;
(b) Subjecting the suspension of Azithromycin monohydrate to stirring/agitation in presence of a mixture of at least one solvent such as herein described and water till non-hygroscopic crystals of Azithromycin dihydrate are obtained.
